data.description: We are delighted to present you with a rare opportunity to rent a classic home in the heart of Terrell Heights. This is a unique property with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, ideal for those who need extra space for work or creativity. The highlight of this home is the black iron spiral staircase that takes you to the upper level, where you will find a spacious loft that can be used as a bedroom, office or studio. This loft has a custom design and plenty of natural light. The kitchen is equipped with a gas stove that is ideal for cooking. The home also comes with a washer, dryer and refrigerator. The living area is spacious and bright, with beautiful natural lighting. The home has an oversized utility room inside and a shed in the backyard that has electricity. You can use the shed as a workshop or storage space. The tenant benefit package, it includes A/C filters, renter's insurance and more. Please note that there are some pet restrictions. Dishwasher, Granite Countertops, Oven, Refrigerator, Carpet, Ceramic Tile, Dining Room, Laundry Room, Living Room, Primary Bath, Primary Bedroom, Air Conditioning, Dryer, Storage, Vaulted Ceilings, Washer, Deck / Balcony, Fence, Shed & Playground.
